idth":2000,"height":1125,"file_path":"/3ZUQ5aqzfnA5qwRK35jx1ia59qY.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":2024,"height":1139,"file_path":"/jtO9vsvW5e03IQUNroyYK3ZVoDF.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":2000,"height":1125,"file_path":"/9KWkXMUnR1kNgBwnwpqUtnsWUgw.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T05:56:56.869+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"A comedy so big it'll leave you breathless.","homepage":"https://anacondamovie.com","overview":"A group of friends facing mid-life crises head to the rainforest with the intention of remaking their favorite movie from their youth, only to find themselves in a fight for their lives against natural disasters, giant snakes and violent criminals."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"아나콘다","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"중년의 위기를 겪고 있는 친구들이 젊은 시절 가장 좋아했던 영화를 재현하기 위해 열대우림으로 떠난다. 그러나 그들은 자연 재해, 거대한 뱀, 그리고 폭력적인 범죄자들과 맞서 싸우며 생존을 위한 사투를 벌이게 된다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Gros enjeux. Très gros serpents.","homepage":"https://anacondamovie.com/","overview":"Doug et Griff sont amis d'enfance et partagent depuis toujours un objectif un peu fou : réaliser leur propre remake d’Anaconda en plein cœur de l'Amazonie. Mais le rêve vire rapidement au cauchemar lorsqu'un véritable serpent géant fait son apparition et transforme leur plateau déjà chaotique en un piège mortel. Le film qu'ils mourraient d'envie de faire… va vraiment devenir mortel !"},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Una aventura que te dejará temblando.","homepage":"https://www.sonypictures.es/pelicula/anaconda-pelicula","overview":"Doug y Griff son muy buenos amigos desde que eran niños y siempre han soñado con hacer un remake de su película favorita de todos los tiempos: el «clásico cinematográfico» Anaconda. Cuando una crisis de mediana edad les anima a lanzarse por fin a la aventura, se adentran en la selva amazónica para empezar a rodar. Pero las cosas se ponen serias cuando aparece una anaconda gigante de verdad, convirtiendo su caótico y cómico plató de rodaje en una situación mortal."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Doug y Griff, amigos de toda la vida, atraviesan una crisis de mediana edad y deciden realizar el remake de su película favorita de su juventud: Anaconda (1997). Viajan a la selva amazónica para filmar su versión, pero pronto descubren que una anaconda real los acecha, convirtiendo su proyecto cinematográfico en una lucha por sobrevivir. La película combina comedia, acción y terror en una experiencia cinematográfica única."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Đụng Độ Siêu Trăn","runtime":0,"tagline":"Một bộ phim họ muốn quay \"gần chết\".","homepage":"","overview":"Một nhóm bạn thân đang khủng hoảng tuổi trung niên quyết định lên đường vào rừng rậm để làm lại bộ phim yêu thích thời trẻ. Nhưng hành trình hoài niệm nhanh chóng biến thành cuộc chiến sinh tồn dữ dội, khi họ phải đối mặt với thiên tai, rắn khổng lồ, và cả những tên tội phạm nguy hiểm."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":105,"tagline":"Você nunca se divertiu com algo tão grande.","homepage":"https://anacondafilme.com.br/home/","overview":"Uma crise de meia-idade inspira Doug e Griff a irem até a floresta amazônica para refazer o filme favorito da juventude, mas tudo muda quando uma anaconda gigante de verdade aparece, transformando o cenário comicamente caótico em uma situação mortal. O filme que eles estão morrendo de vontade de fazer? Pode acabar matando-os."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":0,"tagline":"Komédia, ktorá ti vyrazí dych","homepage":"","overview":"Jack Black a Paul Rudd sa v dobrodružnej komédii plnej napätia a absurdných situácií predstavia ako dvaja najlepší priatelia, ktorých zastihla kríza stredného veku. Rozhodnú sa preto splniť si dávny detský sen - vydať sa do džungle a natočiť vlastnú verziu kultového filmu Anakonda. Bez peňazí, bez štábu a bez najmenšej predstavy, čo ich v divočine čaká, sa púšťajú do dobrodružstva, ktoré rýchlo prerastie do nečakaného boja o prežitie. Obrovská živá anakonda si ich totiž vyhliadla ako ďalšiu korisť a svojho chutného úlovku sa len tak ľahko nevzdá..."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"DIES IST KEIN REBOOT, sondern ist eine völlig neue Komödie, inspiriert vom „Klassiker“ Anaconda, in der Doug und Griff die Hauptrollen spielen. Die beiden sind seit ihrer Kindheit beste Freunde und träumen schon immer davon, ihren absoluten Lieblingsfilm neu zu verfilmen. Ihre Midlife-Crisis treibt sie dazu, ihren Traum endlich in die Tat umzusetzen. Sie reisen tief in den Amazonas, um mit den Dreharbeiten zu beginnen. Doch aus Spaß wird schnell Ernst, als plötzlich eine echte Riesenanaconda auftaucht – und das chaotisch-komische Filmset in eine tödliche Falle verwandelt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Анаконда","runtime":0,"tagline":"Кіно, яке вони знімають, стане реальністю","homepage":"","overview":"Даг і Ґріфф — нерозлучні друзі з дитинства, яких об’єднує шалена мрія: відтворити свій улюблений фільм усіх часів — «легендарну» Анаконду. Криза середнього віку підштовхує їх нарешті ризикнути й вирушити в саме серце Амазонки, щоб розпочати зйомки. Але веселий хаос на майданчику перетворюється на боротьбу за виживання, коли перед ними постає справжня гігантська анаконда. І фільм, за який вони готові «померти», може справді коштувати їм життя…"},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"ანაკონდა","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"新狂蟒之灾","runtime":0,"tagline":"致命翻拍，殊死重启!","homepage":"","overview":"　　一群面临中年危机的朋友前往雨林，打算重拍他们年轻时最喜爱的电影，却意外遭遇自然灾害、巨蟒和凶残罪犯，不得不为生存而殊死搏斗。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"อนาคอนดา เลื้อยสยองโลก","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ดั๊ก (แจ็ค แบล็ค) และกริฟฟ์ (พอล รัดด์) เป็นเพื่อนซี้กันมาตั้งแต่เด็ก พวกเขามีความฝันร่วมกันมาตลอด ในการที่จะรีเมคภาพยนตร์เรื่องโปรดของพวกเขา ภาพยนตร์ขึ้นหิ้งระดับ “คลาสสิค” อนาคอนดา เลื้อยสยองโลก เมื่อวิกฤตวัยกลางคนผลักดันให้เขาลงมือทำมันสักที พวกเขาจึงมุ่งหน้าลึกเข้าไปในป่าแอมะซอน เพื่อเริ่มต้นการถ่ายหนัง แต่ทุกอย่างเริ่มกลายเป็นจริงขึ้นมา เมื่องูยักษ์อนาคอนดาตัวจริงได้ปรากฎขึ้น และทำให้กองถ่ายหนังสุดวายป่วงของพวกเขา ต้องเจอกับสถานการณ์สุดโหดโคตรอันตราย หนังที่พวกเขาอยากสร้างแทบตาย? มันอาจทำให้พวกเขาได้ตายจริงๆก็ได้....."},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"אנקונדה","runtime":0,"tagline":"משהו גדול מגיע.","homepage":"","overview":"דאג וגריף הם החברים הכי טובים מאז שהיו ילדים ותמיד חלמו ליצור מחדש את סרטם האהוב בכל הזמנים: ה-\"קלאסיקה\" הקולנועית 'אנקונדה'. כשמשבר אמצע החיים דוחף אותם סוף־סוף לנסות, הם יוצאים לעומק האמזונס כדי להתחיל בצילומים- אבל העניינים מסתבכים כשהם נתקלים באנקונדה אמיתית. מה שהתחיל כסט צילומים פרוע ומצחיק, הופך במהרה למאבק הישרדות קטלני. הסרט שהם כל כך רוצים ליצור, עלול לעלות להם בחיים..."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"大蟒蛇","runtime":99,"tagline":"你後面有蛇！","homepage":"","overview":"道格和格里夫自小就是最要好的朋友，他們一直夢想能重拍他們最喜愛的「經典」電影【大蟒蛇】。當中年危機推動他們決定放手一搏時，他們深入亞馬遜叢林開始拍攝。然而，當真正的巨蟒現身時，原本滑稽混亂的片場瞬間變成致命戰場。他們夢寐以求想完成的電影，可能真的會要了他們的命……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Un'avventura così non l'avete mai vista","homepage":"","overview":"Doug e Griff sono migliori amici fin dall’infanzia e hanno sempre sognato di rifare il loro film preferito di tutti i tempi: il “classico” cinematografico Anaconda. Quando una crisi di mezza età li spinge a buttarsi finalmente nell’impresa, partono per le profondità dell’Amazzonia per iniziare le riprese. Ma le cose si fanno serie quando appare improvvisamente una vera anaconda gigante, trasformando il loro set caotico e comico in in una trappola mortale. Il film che muoiono dalla voglia di girare? Potrebbe letteralmente ucciderli..."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"狂蟒之災","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Doug（積伯克 飾）同Griff（保羅活特 飾）由細癲到大，最大夢想就係重拍最愛「經典神作」《狂蟒之災》！中年危機大爆發，兩個麻甩佬的起心肝，衝入亞馬遜熱帶雨林開機拍攝。點知拍拍下居然有條真・巨蟒現身，將荒謬混亂片場變成生死一線間的殺戮戰場！搏老命想拍成嘅「世紀傑作」⋯今次真係可能攞佢哋命！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Анаконда","runtime":0,"tagline":"«Она ближе, чем кажется»","homepage":"","overview":"Группа друзей отправляется в джунгли, чтобы снять ремейк «Анаконды», их любимого фильма юности. Однако вскоре после начала съёмок змея, главная звезда фильма, погибает, и друзьям приходится продвигаться в глубь джунглей, чтобы найти ей замену."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"He haluavat kuollakseen tehdä tämän leffan uusiksi","homepage":"","overview":"Doug ja Griff ovat olleet parhaat ystävykset lapsuudesta asti – ja haaveilleet aina tekevänsä uuden version lempi”klassikko”elokuvastaan, Anacondasta. Kun keski-iän kriisi sysää heidät vihdoin toteuttamaan unelmansa, suuntaavat kaverukset syvälle Amazonin viidakkoon aloittamaan kuvaukset. Mutta pian homma muuttuu vakavaksi, kun paikalle ilmestyy oikea jättiläisanaconda ja kaoottisesta komediakuvausryhmästä tulee hengenvaarassa selviytyvä joukko. Elokuvaprojekti, jonka puolesta he olisivat valmiita vaikka kuolemaan – saattaa todella koitua heidän kohtalokseen..."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":0,"tagline":"Nevetni kötelező, menekülni ajánlott","homepage":"","overview":"Az 1997-ben megjelent Anakonda című thriller humoros újragondolása. Egy baráti társaság épp a életközépi válsággal néz szembe. Úgy döntenek, hogy újra elkészítik fiatalkori kedvenc filmjüket, az Anakondát. Amikor azonban nekivágnak a dzsungelnek, hogy ott forgassanak, a dolgok rövidesen kicsúsznak a kezükből, és a helyzet meglepően valóságossá és veszélyessé válik.  (Csillag Lajos)"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"آناکوندا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"داستان حول گروهی از دوستان می‌چرخد که در میانه‌ی بحران ‌میانسالی هستند و تصمیم می‌گیرند نسخه‌ای جدید از یک فیلم ترسناک محبوب دوران نوجوانی‌شان بسازند. آن‌ها برای فیلم‌برداری پروژه‌شان به جنگل آمازون می‌روند، اما با رویدادهای غیرمنتظره‌ای روبه‌رو می‌شوند؛ از جمله اینکه با یک آناکُندای واقعی مواجه می‌شوند که شکارشان می‌کند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Grupa prijatelja suočenih s krizom srednjih godina odlazi u prašumu s namjerom da prerade svoj omiljeni film iz mladosti, samo da bi se našli u borbi za život protiv prirodnih katastrofa, divovskih zmija i nasilnih kriminalaca."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"एनाकोंडा","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":99,"tagline":"Une comédie tellement géniale qu'elle va te couper le souffle.","homepage":"https://www.sonypictures.ca/fr/films/anaconda","overview":"Doug et Griff, deux meilleurs amis d’enfance, ont toujours rêvé de faire un remake de leur film préféré : le « classique » du cinéma, Anaconda. En pleine crise de la cinquantaine, ils décident de se lancer et voyagent au cœur de l'Amazonie pour commencer le tournage. Mais les choses tournent mal lorsqu'un vrai anaconda géant fait son apparition, transformant leur plateau de tournage sympa et chaotique en un piège mortel. Le film qu'ils rêvent de réaliser ? Il pourrait bien leur coûter la vie..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Анаконда","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Анаконда разказва за двама приятели? – Дъг (Блек) и Гриф (Ръд), които са твърдо решени да отдадат почит към любимия си филм от младостта – „кинокласиката“ Анаконда. Те се отправят на пътешествие дълбоко в Амазонка, за да заснемат своя собствена версия на филма, но това, което започва като шеговито носталгично приключение, бързо се превръща в смъртоносно изпитание – на сцената излиза истинска гигантска анаконда, която започва да сее смърт и ужас на снимачната им площадка. Може би точно филмът, който си умират да направят, ще ги погуби."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":0,"tagline":"Yeniden çekmeyi ölümüne istedikleri film.","homepage":"","overview":"Yıllardır en sevdikleri film olan Anakonda'yı yeniden çekmenin hayalini kuran iki arkadaş Doug ve Griff, orta yaş krizine girdikleri bir dönemde büyük hayallerini gerçekleştirmek için bir maceraya atılırlar."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"Een komedie zo groots dat je er ademloos van raakt.","homepage":"","overview":"Doug en Griff zijn al sinds hun jeugd beste vrienden en hebben er altijd van gedroomd om ooit een remake te maken van hun favoriete film: de ‘klassieker’ Anaconda. Aangedreven door een midlifecrisis besluiten ze om hun droom eindelijk waar te maken en trekken ze diep het Amazonegebied in om te gaan filmen. Maar als ze daar op een echte reuzenanaconda stuiten, verandert de komische chaos van hun filmset in een levensgevaarlijke situatie. De film van hun leven zou ze zomaar het leven kunnen kosten..."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":100,"tagline":"Komedie tak velkolepá, že vám vyrazí dech.","homepage":"","overview":"Doug a Griff jsou nejlepšími přáteli už od dětství a vždy snili o tom, že natočí remake svého nejoblíbenějšího filmu: filmové „klasiky“ Anaconda. Když je krize středního věku donutí konečně se do toho pustit, vydávají se hluboko do Amazonie, aby začali natáčet. Celá  situace se zkomplikuje, když se objeví skutečná obří anakonda, která promění jejich komicky chaotické filmové natáčení ve smrtelně nebezpečnou situaci. Film, který tak touží natočit - je může stát život..."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Ett äventyr så stort att det ssslukar dig","homepage":"","overview":"Doug och Griff har varit bästa vänner sedan de var små och har alltid drömt om att göra en ny version av sin absoluta favoritfilm, \"Anaconda\". När en medelålderskris får dem att äntligen göra slag i saken, beger de sig långt in i Amazonas för att börja filma. Men det blir allvar när en verklig jättelik anakonda dyker upp och förvandlar deras komiskt kaotiska filminspelning till en livsfarlig situation. Filmen som de är dödssugna på att göra kanske faktiskt kostar dem livet ..."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"俺たちのアナコンダ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un grup de artiști de circ care se îndreaptă spre ceea ce ei cred că este o nouă locație de spectacol, rămân blocați într-o pădure tropicală după ce barca în care se aflau e atacată de un șarpe anaconda, iar căpitanul este ucis. Ei se întâlnesc cu un braconier tenace care vânează astfel de șerpi și care își dă seama că acum ar putea avea suficientă momeală pentru a-l prinde. Dar, fiind artiști de circ, ei au câteva trucuri de supraviețuire în mânecă."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":99,"tagline":"Komedia tak wielka, że ​​zapiera dech w piersiach.","homepage":"","overview":"Doug i Griff są najlepszymi przyjaciółmi od dzieciństwa i zawsze marzyli o nakręceniu remake'u swojego ulubionego filmu wszech czasów: kinowego klasyka - \"Anakonda\". Kiedy kryzys wieku średniego popycha ich do podjęcia tego wyzwania, wyruszają w głąb Amazonii, aby rozpocząć zdjęcia. Jednak sytuacja staje się poważna, gdy pojawia się prawdziwa gigantyczna anakonda, zamieniając ich komicznie chaotyczny plan filmowy w śmiertelnie niebezpieczne miejsce. Film, który tak bardzo chcą nakręcić? Może właśnie doprowadzić ich do śmierci..."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Ανακόντα","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Δύο κολλητοί φίλοι, ο Doug (Jack Black) και o Griff (Paul Rudd), πάντα ονειρεύονταν να ξαναγυρίσουν την αγαπημένη τους ταινία, το θρυλικό Ανακόντα. Όταν η κρίση μέσης ηλικίας τούς ωθεί να το τολμήσουν επιτέλους, ταξιδεύουν στα βάθη του Αμαζονίου. Όμως τα πράγματα σοβαρεύουν όταν εμφανίζεται ένα πραγματικό γιγάντιο ανακόντα, μετατρέποντας το ήδη χαοτικό σετ σε θανατηφόρα παγίδα. Η ταινία που πεθαίνουν να φτιάξουν μπορεί τελικά να τους σκοτώσει."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":0,"tagline":"Umirajo od želje, da bi poustvarili ta film.","homepage":"","overview":"Skupina prijateljev, ki se soočajo s krizo srednjih let, se odpravi v deževni pragozd z namenom, da bi ponovno posneli svoj najljubši film iz mladosti, le da se znajdejo v boju za preživetje proti naravnim nesrečam, orjaškim kačam in nasilnim kriminalcem."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Анаконда","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"","iso_639_1":"mk","iso_3166_1":"MK","english_name":"Macedonian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Doug e Griff , dois amigos de longa data, partilham um sonho: refazer o clássico Anaconda. O plano? Aventurarem-se pela Amazónia e filmarem o seu próprio remake, com mais entusiasmo do que preparação. O que começa por um sonho de amigos rapidamente se transforma numa hilariante aventura repleta de... imprevistos."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Barndomsvennerne Doug (Jack Black) og Griff (Paul Rudd) kaster sig endelig ud i deres længe nærede drøm om at genindspille deres yndlingskultklassiker, Anaconda, i Amazonas' dybder. Men kaoset bliver alvor, da en ægte kæmpeanaconda dukker op og forvandler deres komiske filmoptagelse til en dødsensfarlig situation. Filmen, de brænder for at lave? Den kan ende med at koste dem livet..."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"أناكوندا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"مجموعة من الأصدقاء الذين يواجهون أزمات منتصف العمر يتوجهون إلى الغابة المطيرة بنية إعادة إنتاج فيلمهم المفضل من شبابهم، ليجدوا أنفسهم في صراع من أجل البقاء على قيد الحياة في مواجهة الكوارث الطبيعية والثعابين العملاقة والمجرمين العنيفين."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"أناكوندا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"تدور احداث الفيلم وسط معاناة أزمة منتصف العمر، تقرر مجموعة من الأصدقاء التعاون معًا في سبيل إنتاج نسخة حديثة من فيلمهم المفضل بفترة الشباب، ولكن تقودهم الرحلة إلى مجموعة من الأحداث الغير متوقعة بالأدغال."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Анаконда","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Група пријатеља који се суочавају са кризом средњих година креће ка прашуми са намером да сниме нову верзију свог омиљеног филма из младости, само да би се нашли у борби за живот против природних катастрофа, џиновских змија и насилних криминалаца."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Anakonda","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Grupė draugų, išgyvenančių vidurio amžiaus krizę, leidžiasi į atogrąžų miškus su tikslu perkurti savo jaunystės mėgstamą filmą. Tačiau netrukus jie atsiduria kovoje už savo gyvybes, susidurdami su gamtos stichijomis, milžiniškomis gyvatėmis ir žiauriais nusikaltėliais. Kelionė, turėjusi būti nostalgijos pilna avantiūra, virsta tikru išgyvenimo išbandymu, kur kiekvienas žingsnis gali būti paskutinis."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sekelompok teman yang menghadapi krisis paruh baya pergi ke hutan hujan dengan tujuan membuat ulang film favorit mereka sejak masa muda, hanya untuk mendapati diri mereka berjuang demi hidup mereka melawan bencana alam, ular raksasa, dan penjahat kejam."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"695036c24e3a808d7bfb1466","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/695036c24e3a808d7bfb1466","author":"Manuel São Bento","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-12-27T19:42:58.107Z","updated_at":"2025-12-27T19:42:58.133Z","author_details":{"name":"Manuel São Bento","rating":6,"username":"msbreviews","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"6954096c01fdd85625e42108","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6954096c01fdd85625e42108","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$12","created_at":"2025-12-30T17:18:36.432Z","updated_at":"2025-12-30T19:17:51.174Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":6,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}},{"id":"69973796723fa640756f690c","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/69973796723fa640756f690c","author":"Enes","content":"It was more fun than scary. Especially the scene at the end where the guy shows off his actions in public as an achievement was great 😂 I liked it and it's definitely worth watching. The acting is fantastic, the effects are good, and the script is entertaining. I think it deserves a 7 out of 10. Thank you for your hard work.","created_at":"2026-02-19T16:17:26.520Z","updated_at":"2026-02-19T16:17:26.527Z","author_details":{"name":"Enes","rating":7,"username":"Eness_","avatar_path":"/wASOrU1PJmMuTD1jIdop9yBvYdh.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[{"id":10225,"adult":false,"title":"Friday the 13th Part VI: Jason Lives","video":false,"overview":"Tommy Jarvis, tormented by the fear that maybe Jason isn't really dead, unwittingly resurrects the mass murderer for another bloody rampage.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":3.4053,"vote_count":1315,"poster_path":"/6vdUpHvkspQonXBdWcLWW5ciEPJ.jpg","release_date":"1986-08-01","vote_average":6.252,"backdrop_path":"/93tvkTtV6tQQiYhxhij9tuODNOq.jpg","original_title":"Friday the 13th Part VI: Jason Lives","original_language":"en"},{"id":10227,"adult":false,"title":"PlayTime","video":false,"overview":"Clumsy Monsieur Hulot finds himself perplexed by the intimidating complexity of a gadget-filled Paris. He attempts to meet with a business contact but soon becomes lost. His roundabout journey parallels that of an American tourist, and as they weave through the inventive urban environment, they intermittently meet, developing an interest in one another. They eventually get together at a chaotic restaurant, along with several other quirky characters.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":2.9307,"vote_count":642,"poster_path":"/kQOrS0DLUXYsqPMedM2G6NJcJBq.jpg","release_date":"1967-12-13","vote_average":7.728,"backdrop_path":"/ynz9uQBiNGojJzpxhpbGDXkpTP.jpg","original_title":"PlayTime","original_language":"fr"},{"id":279641,"adult":false,"title":"Whiskey Tango Foxtrot","video":false,"overview":"In 2002, cable news producer Kim Barker decides to shake up her routine by taking a daring new assignment in Kabul, Afghanistan. Dislodged from her comfortable American lifestyle, Barker finds herself in the middle of an out-of-control war zone. Luckily, she meets Tanya Vanderpoel, a fellow journalist who takes the shell-shocked reporter under her wing. Amid the militants, warlords and nighttime partying, Barker discovers the key to becoming a successful correspondent.","genre_ids":[35,18,10752],"popularity":1.0251,"vote_count":1027,"poster_path":"/xhWbp0lCig5vkdFZPiOGNRL9oMf.jpg","release_date":"2016-03-04","vote_average":6.311,"backdrop_path":"/7295GnkwMbNcHLEXkQkLNIWNa39.jpg","original_title":"Whiskey Tango Foxtrot","original_language":"en"},{"id":10243,"adult":false,"title":"The Flight of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"A cargo aircraft crashes in a sandstorm in the Sahara with less than a dozen men on board. One of the passengers is an airplane designer who comes up with the idea of ripping off the undamaged wing and using it as the basis for a replacement aircraft they need to build before their food and water run out.","genre_ids":[12,18],"popularity":1.5891,"vote_count":358,"poster_path":"/zrzLl7NWdjwGhVE7bqpOAxMVtF.jpg","release_date":"1965-12-15","vote_average":7.214,"backdrop_path":"/61cz8dZkyIo9m5bVwwfrYcvVZiK.jpg","original_title":"The Flight of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":10328,"adult":false,"title":"Cocoon","video":false,"overview":"When a group of trespassing seniors swim in a pool containing alien cocoons, they find themselves energized with youthful vigor.","genre_ids":[35,878,9648,18],"popularity":2.2818,"vote_count":1374,"poster_path":"/wqNNm36j3nkucAucHEGAW5pNZcd.jpg","release_date":"1985-06-21","vote_average":6.628,"backdrop_path":"/SOROsJCXjEkeJ9zohXi7lEC58R.jpg","original_title":"Cocoon","original_language":"en"},{"id":10330,"adult":false,"title":"Freaky Friday","video":false,"overview":"Mother and daughter bicker over everything -- what Anna wears, whom she likes and what she wants to do when she's older. In turn, Anna detests Tess's fiancé. When a magical fortune cookie switches their personalities, they each get a peek at how the other person feels, thinks and lives.","genre_ids":[10751,14,35,10749],"popularity":5.4821,"vote_count":4198,"poster_path":"/ipKcZ4Up7dp18XpsfYUc9NKZy3g.jpg","release_date":"2003-08-05","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/aH4MrSu8fwjRiEMGfdRwpsYu2PW.jpg","original_title":"Freaky Friday","original_language":"en"},{"id":10377,"adult":false,"title":"My Cousin Vinny","video":false,"overview":"Two carefree pals traveling through rural Alabama on their way back to college are mistakenly arrested and charged with murder. Fortunately, one of them has a cousin who's a lawyer - Vincent Gambini, a former auto mechanic from Brooklyn who has just passed his bar exam after his sixth try. When he arrives with his leather-clad girlfriend to try his first case, it's a real shock - for him and the Deep South!","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":3.7746,"vote_count":1803,"poster_path":"/iwSURa8nS2ujwrU3s1lfxxX7voH.jpg","release_date":"1992-03-13","vote_average":7.504,"backdrop_path":"/uEoaOfvWibpvjBNxFoj4MxWn0OH.jpg","original_title":"My Cousin Vinny","original_language":"en"},{"id":10378,"adult":false,"title":"Big Buck Bunny","video":false,"overview":"Follow a day of the life of Big Buck Bunny when he meets three bullying rodents: Frank, Rinky, and Gamera. The rodents amuse themselves by harassing helpless creatures by throwing fruits, nuts and rocks at them. After the deaths of two of Bunny's favorite butterflies, and an offensive attack on Bunny himself, Bunny sets aside his gentle nature and orchestrates a complex plan for revenge.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751],"popularity":0.5638,"vote_count":194,"poster_path":"/i9jJzvoXET4D9pOkoEwncSdNNER.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-10","vote_average":6.497,"backdrop_path":"/xtdybjRRZ15mCrPOvEld305myys.jpg","original_title":"Big Buck Bunny","original_language":"en"},{"id":10379,"adult":false,"title":"Drop Dead Fred","video":false,"overview":"An unhappy housewife gets a lift from the return of her imaginary childhood friend, Drop Dead Fred.","genre_ids":[35,14,10751],"popularity":1.2893,"vote_count":391,"poster_path":"/v2kadCRcRdq8a0aRbQg4yVk3Xmd.jpg","release_date":"1991-04-19","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/h8EZTu4ZqzTsXWo7N14t8qEj3gN.jpg","original_title":"Drop Dead Fred","original_language":"en"},{"id":10253,"adult":false,"title":"Dragon Wars: D-War","video":false,"overview":"Ethan learns he carries the spirit of a warrior who battled dragons in 16th-century Korea -- and one day he'll find a tattooed girl carrying the spirit of that warrior's beloved. Years later, he meets Sarah and dragons soon descend on Los Angeles seeking out the two souls of the ancient lovers.","genre_ids":[14,18,27,28,53,878],"popularity":1.5775,"vote_count":444,"poster_path":"/rEpvqWGu08coDLUpcpiz4sMoDYo.jpg","release_date":"2007-08-01","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/5WWqrUIGrCb1QvZtYVaSfZgUG8n.jpg","original_title":"디 워","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1259984,"adult":false,"title":"Macadamia","video":false,"overview":"A one-hour stand-up show where Nacho Redondo deploys a universe full of black humor without concessions, where censorship is not a variable at stake, where being silent so as not to bother is not a possibility.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.1639,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/s4djvwhKejlb1Zh8YYlYGw7OUzc.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-22","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/mJ6Xi0hFM6jUrRopTA6i3xAXfrZ.jpg","original_title":"Macadamia","original_language":"es"},{"id":1260004,"adult":false,"title":"Island of Death","video":false,"overview":"Dara disregarded her mother's prohibition to celebrate graduation with Pandu, Niki, Lathi, and Noah on a ship. Unbeknownst to them, their ship stranded on an unnamed island. Longing enveloped Dara for her mother as she and her friends were trapped there. Can Dara and her friends escape from the island?","genre_ids":[12,27],"popularity":4.067,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/5Rvs6cM1yZs7iGRlpZNj7o2yFtK.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-10","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/xdWp1LpiutVD79d9E68JaHrltU9.jpg","original_title":"Pulau Hantu","original_language":"id"},{"id":10464,"adult":false,"title":"Corrina, Corrina","video":false,"overview":"When Manny Singer's wife dies, his young daughter Molly becomes mute and withdrawn. To help cope with looking after Molly, he hires sassy housekeeper Corrina Washington, who coaxes Molly out of her shell and shows father and daughter a whole new way of life. Manny and Corrina's friendship delights Molly and enrages the other townspeople.","genre_ids":[35,10751,10749],"popularity":1.2497,"vote_count":446,"poster_path":"/xuEubxRGut2Yh118RyNa6ruXXCp.jpg","release_date":"1994-08-12","vote_average":6.689,"backdrop_path":"/uFh5qOyctqOOuEayOOoukE8CkV9.jpg","original_title":"Corrina, Corrina","original_language":"en"},{"id":10466,"adult":false,"title":"The Money Pit","video":false,"overview":"After being evicted from their Manhattan apartment, a couple buy what looks like the home of their dreams—only to find themselves saddled with a bank-account-draining nightmare. Struggling to keep their relationship together as their rambling mansion falls to pieces around them, the two watch in hilarious horror as everything—including the kitchen sink—disappears into the Money Pit.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":3.0041,"vote_count":1214,"poster_path":"/bohhidIi1WWU5NNYF9l5wLQu3Ii.jpg","release_date":"1986-03-26","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/2C2kUFxhs5u2G9xeg4KQ0FZvFFA.jpg","original_title":"The Money Pit","original_language":"en"},{"id":279988,"adult":false,"title":"Extinction","video":false,"overview":"Deep in the Amazon jungle a group of scientists are on a dangerous mission. When their guide suddenly abandons them, they find themselves in a savage and hostile environment. However, things turn deadly when they find they are in the middle of a hunting ground for a pack of prehistoric predators long thought extinct.","genre_ids":[53,12],"popularity":3.1294,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/13LTZkxrAkswx2eidHK06XbVH8n.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-24","vote_average":3.8,"backdrop_path":"/18qzbskGhbAPjkFrtgPw1utxIF0.jpg","original_title":"Extinction","original_language":"en"},{"id":10480,"adult":false,"title":"Nurse Betty","video":false,"overview":"What happens when a person decides that life is merely a state of mind? If you're Betty, a small-town waitress and soap opera fan from Fair Oaks, Kansas, you refuse to believe that you can't be with the love of your life just because he doesn't really exist. After all, life is no excuse for not living. Traumatized by a savage event, Betty enters into a fugue state that allows -- even encourages -- her to keep functioning... in a kind of alternate reality.","genre_ids":[35,80,53],"popularity":1.1327,"vote_count":424,"poster_path":"/1OCHR9z9k7go669AsShOkTj4CFb.jpg","release_date":"2000-08-30","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/8ZquU1oL90wNowQeXaXx7xPk7vZ.jpg","original_title":"Nurse Betty","original_language":"en"},{"id":10489,"adult":false,"title":"Cujo","video":false,"overview":"A friendly St. Bernard named \"Cujo\" contracts rabies and conducts a reign of terror on a small American town.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":2.6151,"vote_count":1103,"poster_path":"/uNBt2YxrQdyOjnm2rDQ5QiCmQ0K.jpg","release_date":"1983-08-10","vote_average":6.152,"backdrop_path":"/hK19fcSgkAN6de6HlsJVlPYncwv.jpg","original_title":"Cujo","original_language":"en"},{"id":10344,"adult":false,"title":"The Fly II","video":false,"overview":"Martin Brundle, born of the human/fly, is adopted by his father's place of employment (Bartok Inc.) while the employees simply wait for his mutant chromosomes to come out of their dormant state.","genre_ids":[27,878],"popularity":1.6251,"vote_count":708,"poster_path":"/gORksEPahEgO409HYJOZlNVyEpe.jpg","release_date":"1989-02-10","vote_average":5.701,"backdrop_path":"/vj8ZmAqj6QZMQ6K12VXoLaPOagr.jpg","original_title":"The Fly II","original_language":"en"},{"id":10357,"adult":false,"title":"Volcano","video":false,"overview":"An earthquake shatters a peaceful Los Angeles morning and opens a fissure deep into the earth, causing lava to start bubbling up. As a volcano begins forming in the La Brea Tar Pits, the director of the city's emergency management service, working with a geologist, must then use every resource in the city to try and stop the volcano from consuming LA.","genre_ids":[878,28,18,53],"popularity":4.3331,"vote_count":1633,"poster_path":"/5xIjktjXuro7anZ6AR58t5ZYWjQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-04-25","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/lYpScP0hkba0X3HY1VrKZ7LOMxS.jpg","original_title":"Volcano","original_language":"en"},{"id":10447,"adult":false,"title":"No Escape","video":false,"overview":"In the year 2022, a ruthless prison warden has created the ultimate solution for his most troublesome and violent inmates: Absolom, a secret jungle island where prisoners are abandoned and left to die. But Marine Captain John Robbins, convicted of murdering a commanding officer, is determined to escape the island 